The paper discusses the issue of adversarial attacks in deep neural networks, which is a common topic in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and cryptography (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper proposes a method to increase the robustness of neural networks, which falls under the sub-field of neural networks (cs.NE).
